  "pet - bubbles": {  
      "title":"Fishing Pet - Bubbles",
      "description":"[Bubbles pet](https://runescape.wikia.com/wiki/Bubbles_pet) is an item that can be found while training Fishing. It can be used to unlock [Bubbles](https://runescape.wikia.com/wiki/Bubbles).",
      "url":"https://runescape.wikia.com/wiki/Bubbles",
      "color":12269891,
      "footer":{  
         "icon_url":"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/297388220231057419/400471386101121024/image.jpg",
         "text":"Achievement Help | Helping you reach your goals, whatever they may be!"
      },
      "thumbnail":{  
         "url":"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/runescape2/images/1/1f/Bubbles_%28pet%29.png/revision/latest/scale-to-width-down/200?cb=20160823222200"
      },
      "author":{  
         "name":"Max Cape Info",
         "icon_url":"https://i.imgur.com/6c6q2iC.png"
      },
      "fields":[  
         {  
            "name":"Methods to obtain",
            "value":"• Net Fishing\n• Crayfish cage Fishing\n• Fishing rod Fishing\n• Bait Fishing\n• Fly fishing rod Fishing\n• Feather Fishing\n• Lure Fishing\n• Harpoons\n• Cages\n• Barbarian Fishing\n• Prifddinas Waterfall Fishing\n• Fishing in The Arc\n• Fishing Frenzy at Deep Sea Fishing"
         },
         {  
            "name":"Best method",
            "value":"• Fishing Frenzy at Deep Sea Fishing\n• Crystallise Menaphos Fishing"
         },
         {  
            "name":"Methods which do not work",
            "value":"• Fish Flingers\n• Gathering from divine locations"
         },
         {  
            "name":"Formula",
            "value":"Gaining this pet is based on the amount of experience drops received, not the size of the experience drops. Therefore, it is best to choose a method among the fastest experience drops.\n\nIn a purely mathematical format your chance (f) of receiving a pet on any particular action is:\nf = T *S / 50,000,000\n\nWhere:\n*T* is the amount of game ticks taken per action\n*S* is the virtual skill level. At 200 million experience, a flat bonus of 50 is applied to this value"
         }
      ]
   },
